<table width=75%>
<tr><td bgcolor="#0000AF">
<strong><font color=white>
<center>Crafted Bracers Quest</center>
</font></strong>
</td></tr>
</table><BR>
<div align="left">
1) Obtain the quest from Ulan.  Ulan is in the centaur village at approximately 0 by -2100.<BR>
<BR>
2) Obtain a bundle of optic nerves from an evil eye from East Karana or Beholder's Maze.<BR>
<BR>
3) Buy one sapphire.<BR>
<BR>
4) Give the nerves and the sapphire to Ulan for a Crafted Bracer.</div>
<BR>
